Package org.jboss.windup.ast.java

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BatchASTFuture
    Used for the AST Processor to indicate that it is done processing.
    BatchASTListener
    Provides a callback to indicate that processing has completed for a particular file.
    WildcardImportResolver
    Provides a pluggable lookup mechanism for resolving wildcard imports.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASTProcessor  
    BatchASTProcessor
    Processes multiple files at a time in order to improve performance.
    NoopWildcardImportResolver
    Provides a default implementation of WildcardImportResolver resolver that does no actual resolution.
    ReferenceResolvingVisitor
    Provides the ability to parse a Java source file and return a List of ClassReference objects containing the fully qualified names of all of the contained references.
    ReferenceResolvingVisitorState  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ASTException
    Thrown due to errors parsing Java source with the ASTReferenceResolver
